name: Fast Toys
description: This holiday season, fast toys are popular,  from skis to mountain bikes to supercars, the best gear needs lightweight materials!

name: Three Amigos
description: (2019) The county fair is holding a contest for teams of 3 farmers to win big prizes!

name: Space Vacation
description: (2019) Space Tourism is way up this year and there are rocket fuel shortages everywhere!

name: Teslegg Model F
description: (2019) After a long wait Teslegg has released their mass market fusion powered car! Fusion eggs are in high demand.

name: Through The Snow
description: Shipping prices are up due to weather, but medical suppliers are offering bonuses!

name: Storage Storage
description: (2022) With a large decrease in container shipping, ports are building massive quantum warehouses to store the empty storage containers - orders are in!

name: Back To School
description: (2018) Back-to-school students are in need of a refresher, Teachers need tachyon eggs to send kids back in time to review material they forgot over summer.

name: Pre-Diet
description: (2021) This year, pre-dieting to prepare for the holiday season feasts is the trend, and what better way than with Superfood Eggs. Stores are sold out!

name: Family Function
description: Tachyon eggs were needed for a wide array of products this season, to spend more (or less) time with family. Resupply orders are in!

name: Choc Shock
description: An unexpected rush for mother's day chocolates has sent producers scrambling to fill orders - so they're sweetening the deal...

name: Pumpkin Pie
description: (2019) It's that time of year, when what is widely considered the greatest pie hits center stage: Pumpkin Pie.

name: Quantitative Egging
description: (2020) The economy is taking a hit and the government is buying up loads of eggs to keep everyone afloat!

name: Palisades Forever
description: Houses have burned to the ground, but the community is unbroken - they'll want to rebuild with the latest materials!

name: Egg Muscle
description: (2021) Bodybuilders are switching to Superfood Egg diets after discovering a new Amino Acid in the egg. Orders are surging!

name: Laurel vs Yanny
description: (2018) A Quantum rift is causing people to hear different words in a viral video. Scientists have a fix but they need your help.

name: Ten for Ten
description: (2019) It's a busy time of year for bakers, orders for Edible eggs have quadrupled!

name: New Egglen
description: As more reusable rockets are developed, launch prices decrease, launches increase, and demand for fuel increases!

name: Pumpkin Time!
description: (2019) It is officially Fall (in the northern hemisphere), you know what that means! Pumpkin all the things!

name: Never Enough
description: Stores thought they had enough... there are never enough.

name: Soaking Man
description: (2023) A massive desert arts festival was flooded leaving thousands stranded without enough supplies - Superfood eggs are being air dropped in!

name: Debris Removal
description: A recent disaster has tripled hazardous material removal needs, super capacity carriers use Quantum Eggs to maximize storage.

name: Quantum Monday
description: (2020) With nearly all Holiday shopping happening online, Quantum storage solutions are in high demand!

name: Shipping Surge
description: (2020) A surge in bulk shipping has created an opportunity for quantum egg farmers, join in on the rush!

name: Stuffed
description: (2019) Folks have been over-eating for days and are looking for lighter meals, Superfood eggs are flying off the shelves

name: Backup
description: Home battery backup demands are re-doubling after recent disasters highlighted the need for grid independence

name: Pumpkin Cheesecake
description: (2022) Pumpkin Cheesecake is the trendy desert this Thanksgiving, once again surprising suppliers who need more Pumpkin Eggs!

name: Color Change
description: (2020) As the leaves change color so do the eggs. Help meet seasonal demand!

name: Leftovers
description: (2018) Thanksgiving has left the world with too many leftovers, quantum Tupperware is sold out everywhere, and more raw materials are needed.

name: Sick AF
description: Many are Sick AF, that's right, Sick After Fire - and Medical Egg Technology allows for rapid deployment of targeted drugs!

name: Holidegg
description: (2020) Tasty holiday food and drink such as Egg Nog and Noodle Kugel are spiking demand for regular eggs!

name: Home Renovations
description: (2018) You've decided to build a new house! Why not make it yourself? You'll need a lot of eggs so get started!

name: Last Minute Decoration
description: (2020) Family meetings were called, one common conclusion: We need more pumpkins!

name: Presidential Visit
description: Time tourists are visiting the recent and not-so recent past to remind themselves of the incredible contributions of our Nation's Presidents

name: Black Fried Egg
description: (2022) In store and online deals led to record holiday sales - factories are adding shifts to restock goods - supplies are needed!

name: Quantum Pump
description: From Cities to apartment owners, everyone wants these new hose-less water pumps!

name: R.N.Egg
description: (2022) Gene editing technologies have been adapted to use Immortality Eggs to correct genetic diseases. Supplies are needed!

name: Racing Ramp
description: From Formula 1 to the World Endurance Championship, racing teams are ramping production of new and spare parts!

name: Space Bots
description: (2020) New tiny space robots have been developed to explore space, small enough to be launched with traditional fuels!

name: Fusion Exclusion
description: (2019) Smaller settlements all over the galaxy still use Fusion Egg Reactors and are running short of Fusion Eggs!

name: Hangover Cure
description: (2019) The big new years parties are scheduled, partiers are planning ahead this year and buying hangover cures before hand!

name: Domestic Production
description: Geopolitics have led to increased prices for imports driving some to source alternative - if expensive - materials!

name: Last Minute Shipping
description: (2019) Shipping companies are slammed! More Quantum storage is needed!

name: Anxiety Attack
description: (2018) A new school year and political turmoil have everyone stressed out! A regimen of medical eggs are needed.

name: Winter Break
description: (2018) It's Winter Break! And since break homework was deemed cruel and unusual punishment, Prodigy Eggs are all the rage!

name: Spring Forward Diet
description: Young people love the long evenings, and folks are looking to get trim for increased night life, clean diets are taking off!

name: Water Cup
description: (2022) As the World Cup comes to a close, Quatar's desalination plants are tapped, they have ordered more water!

name: Diapers Everywhere!
description: (2019) The creator of Egg, Inc. (me) just had a baby!  I need y'all to work together to make me some quantum waste pails to help with all the diapers!

name: Pi Day!
description: (2022) With a renewed focus on STEM fields, Pi day has become a worldwide celebration in schools. Projects have cleared out school supplies!

name: Early Easter
description: Easter Egg orders are coming in early this year, as many are trying to get ahead of the price gouging near the day

name: Quantum Payload
description: (2021) With the recent boom in Artifacts exploration, quantum crates are in mass production!
